Alex Jones Show 
February 20 2011

480p video 

[hippie]

On this important Sunday edition of The Alex Jones Show, Alex discusses the developing situation in Libya, Iranian naval ships crossing the Suez canal, thumb scanning to buy and sell goods, the ongoing struggle for freedom in Egypt, and more. Alex also takes takes calls and covers the latest news.
